subtract module¶

subtract.subtract_numbers(a, b)¶

Subtract two numbers and return the result.

Parameters:

  • a (int or float) -- The first number.

  • b (int or float) -- The second number.

Returns:

The subtract of a and b.

Return type:

int or float

Example

>>> subtract_numbers(2, 3)
-1
